## CSS/TailwindCSS Classes

### Custom Classes (when necessary)

**Use kebab-case:**
- `.user-profile`
- `.nav-item-active`
- `.blog-post-card`
- `.article-metadata`

### BEM Notation (for complex components)

```css
/* Block */
.card { }

/* Element */
.card__header { }
.card__body { }
.card__footer { }

/* Modifier */
.card--featured { }
.card--large { }
.card--compact { }
```

```html
<!-- BEM example -->
<div class="card card--featured">
  <div class="card__header">Title</div>
  <div class="card__body">Content</div>
  <div class="card__footer">Footer</div>
</div>
```

### TailwindCSS (Preferred)

```html
<!-- Good: Use Tailwind utilities -->
<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Title</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600">Content</p>
</div>

<!-- Avoid: Custom classes when Tailwind can do it -->
<div class="custom-card">
  <h2 class="custom-title">Title</h2>
</div>
```

